text: Denys Vitaliovich Dubrov (, 10 January 1989 – 9 May 2022)Умер паралимпийский призер Токио-2020 Денис Дубров was a Ukrainian swimmer. At the 2016 Rio Paralympics, he won three gold, three silver and two bronze medals, setting world records in the Men's SM10 200 m individual medleyDenys Dubrov. rio2016.com and S10 100m butterfly events.Ukraine's Denys Dubrov breaks another World Record in Rio ==References== Category:1989 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Ukrainian swimmers Category:Paralympic gold medalists for Ukraine Category:Paralympic silver medalists Category:Paralympic bronze medalists for Ukraine
